Class User

java.lang.Object
user.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<User>
Direct Known Subclasses:
PremiumUser
public class User extends Object implements Comparable<User>, Serializable
The User class represents a user of the application. It implements the Comparable and Serializable interfaces.
